                        + "\n Electron configuration: 1s^2 2s^1 " +"\n Physical Properties" + "\n Phase at STP: Solid" +"\n Melting point: 453.65K" + "\n Boiling point: 1603K" +"\n Density: 0.534g/cm^3(r.t.), 0.512g/cm^3(M.P)");
