                        "\n Electron configuration: 1s^2s^2 " +"\n Physical Properties" + "\n Phase at STP: solid" +"\n Melting point: 1560K" + "\n Boiling point: 2742K" +"\n Density: 1.85g/cm^3(r.t.), 1.690g/cm^3(M.P)");
