                        + "\n Electron configuration: 1s^22s^22p^1 " +"\n Physical Properties" + "\n Phase at STP: solid" +"\n Melting point: 2349K" + "\n Boiling point: 4200K" +"\n Density:2.08g/cm^3(M.P)");
