                        + "\n Electron configuration: 1s^22s^22p^3 " +"\n Physical Properties" + "\n Phase at STP: gas" +"\n Melting point: 63.15K" + "\n Boiling point: 77.355K" +"\n Density: 1.2504g/L(STP), 0.808g/cm^3(B.P)");
