                        + "\n Electron configuration: 1s^22s^22p^6 " +"\n Physical Properties" + "\n Phase at STP: gas" +"\n Melting point: 24.56K" + "\n Boiling point: 27.104K" +"\n Density: 0.9002g/L(STP), 1.207g/cm^3(B.P)");
