                        + "\n Electron configuration: [Ne]3s^1 " +"\n Physical Properties" + "\n Phase at STP: solid" +"\n Melting point: 370.944K" + "\n Boiling point: 1156.090K" +"\n Density: 0.968g/cm^3(near r.t.), 0.927g/cm^3(M.P)");
