                        + "\n Electron configuration: [Ne]3s^23p^1 " +"\n Physical Properties" + "\n Phase at STP: solid" +"\n Melting point: 933.47K" + "\n Boiling point: 2743K" +"\n Density: 2.70g/cm^3(r.t.), 2.375g/cm^3(M.P)");
